  <%= @reservation.car_option? ? @reservation.car_rental : 0 %>円
■ガソリン代:
  <%= @reservation.car_option? ? @reservation.gas : 0 %>円
■高速代:
  <%= @reservation.car_option? ? @reservation.highway : 0 %>円
■パーキング代:
  <%= @reservation.car_option? ? @reservation.parking : 0 %>円
■自転車レンタル代:
  <%= @reservation.bicycle_option? ? @reservation.bicycle_rental : 0 %>円
